The MAIN HTML File is "home_new.html" file.

We can observe the movement of bunny by moving the screen using arrow keys.

Hold the left mouse button and move the mouse for viewing in different angles.

Hold the right mouse button and move the mouse for sliding on the screen.

Please go through the MANUAL before starting the simulation.

Manual consists of clear description of function of each button in the experiment.


---------------------------------------------------------- Details about folders, files and links ----------------------------------------------------------

THE SRIP contains two folders in it, Codes and Libraries.In the "Libraries" folder we have 4 Javascript files required for 3D graphics in Javascript which belong to three.js javascript module.

In the "Codes" folder we have the following:

 >> The main html file is "home_new.html" file

 >> All the CSS files are present in "css" folder

 >> "style.css" file has all the styling for all the html pages

 >> The javascript files are present in the "js" folder

 >> And other htm links are present in "html links" folder.

Read the Manual by clicking on the Manual button provided in the home-page before starting the experiment.